460
461 public void Populate(BestiaryDatabase database)
462 {
463 _currentDatabase = database;
464 AddEmptyEntries_CrittersAndEnemies_Automated();
465 AddTownNPCs_Manual();
466 AddNPCBiomeRelationships_Automated();
467 AddNPCBiomeRelationships_Manual();
468 AddNPCBiomeRelationships_AddDecorations_Automated();
469 ModifyEntriesThatNeedIt();
470 RegisterFilters();
471 RegisterSortSteps();
472 }
473
474 private void RegisterTestEntries()
475 {
476 Register(BestiaryEntry.Biome("Bestiary_Biomes.Hallow", "Images/UI/Bestiary/Biome_Hallow", Conditions.ReachHardMode));
477 }
478
479 private void RegisterSortSteps()
480 {
481 foreach (IBestiarySortStep item in new List<IBestiarySortStep>
482 {
483 new SortingSteps.ByUnlockState(),
484 new SortingSteps.ByBestiarySortingId(),
485 new SortingSteps.Alphabetical(),
486 new SortingSteps.ByNetId(),
487 new SortingSteps.ByAttack(),
488 new SortingSteps.ByDefense(),
489 new SortingSteps.ByCoins(),
490 new SortingSteps.ByHP(),
491 new SortingSteps.ByBestiaryRarity()
492 })
493 {
494 _currentDatabase.Register(item);
495 }
496 }
497
498 private void RegisterFilters()
499 {
500 Register(new Filters.ByUnlockState());
501 Register(new Filters.ByBoss());
502 Register(new Filters.ByRareCreature());
503 List<IBestiaryInfoElement> commonInfoElementsForFilters = CommonTags.GetCommonInfoElementsForFilters();
504 for (int i = 0; i < commonInfoElementsForFilters.Count; i++)
505 {
506 Register(new Filters.ByInfoElement(commonInfoElementsForFilters[i]));
507 }
508 }
509
510 private void ModifyEntriesThatNeedIt_NameOverride(int npcID, string newNameKey)
511 {
512 BestiaryEntry bestiaryEntry = FindEntryByNPCID(npcID);
513 bestiaryEntry.Info.RemoveAll((IBestiaryInfoElement x) => x is NamePlateInfoElement);
514 bestiaryEntry.Info.Add(new NamePlateInfoElement(newNameKey, npcID));
515 bestiaryEntry.Icon = new UnlockableNPCEntryIcon(npcID, 0f, 0f, 0f, 0f, newNameKey);
516 }

679 private void TryGivingEntryFlavorTextIfItIsMissing(BestiaryEntry entry)
680 {
681 if (entry.Info.Any((IBestiaryInfoElement x) => x is FlavorTextBestiaryInfoElement))
682 {
683 return;
684 }
685 SpawnConditionBestiaryInfoElement spawnConditionBestiaryInfoElement = null;
686 int? num = null;
687 foreach (IBestiaryInfoElement item in entry.Info)
688 {
689 if (item is BestiaryPortraitBackgroundProviderPreferenceInfoElement bestiaryPortraitBackgroundProviderPreferenceInfoElement && bestiaryPortraitBackgroundProviderPreferenceInfoElement.GetPreferredProvider() is SpawnConditionBestiaryInfoElement spawnConditionBestiaryInfoElement2)
690 {
691 spawnConditionBestiaryInfoElement = spawnConditionBestiaryInfoElement2;
692 break;
693 }
694 if (item is SpawnConditionBestiaryInfoElement { DisplayTextPriority: var displayTextPriority } spawnConditionBestiaryInfoElement3 && (!num.HasValue || displayTextPriority >= num))
695 {
696 spawnConditionBestiaryInfoElement = spawnConditionBestiaryInfoElement3;
697 num = displayTextPriority;
698 }
699 }
700 if (spawnConditionBestiaryInfoElement != null)
701 {
702 string displayNameKey = spawnConditionBestiaryInfoElement.GetDisplayNameKey();
703 string text = "Bestiary_BiomeText.biome_";
704 string text2 = displayNameKey.Substring(displayNameKey.IndexOf('.') + 1);
705 text += text2;
706 entry.Info.Add(new FlavorTextBestiaryInfoElement(text));
707 }
708 }

719 private void AddEmptyEntries_CrittersAndEnemies_Automated()
720 {
721 HashSet<int> exclusions = GetExclusions();
722 foreach (KeyValuePair<int, NPC> item in ContentSamples.NpcsByNetId)
723 {
724 if (!exclusions.Contains(item.Key))
725 {
726 NPCLoader.SetBestiary(bestiaryEntry: item.Value.CountsAsACritter ? Register(BestiaryEntry.Critter(item.Key)) : ((!item.Value.isLikeATownNPC) ? Register(BestiaryEntry.Enemy(item.Key)) : Register(BestiaryEntry.TownNPC(item.Key))), npc: item.Value, database: _currentDatabase);
727 }
728 }
729 }

731 private static HashSet<int> GetExclusions()
732 {
733 HashSet<int> hashSet = new HashSet<int>();
734 List<int> list = new List<int>();
735 foreach (KeyValuePair<int, NPCID.Sets.NPCBestiaryDrawModifiers> item in NPCID.Sets.NPCBestiaryDrawOffset)
736 {
737 if (item.Value.Hide)
738 {
739 list.Add(item.Key);
740 }
741 }
742 foreach (int item2 in list)
743 {
744 hashSet.Add(item2);
745 }
746 return hashSet;
747 }

1882 private void AddNPCBiomeRelationships_AddDecorations_Automated()
1883 {
1884 foreach (KeyValuePair<int, NPC> item in ContentSamples.NpcsByNetId)
1885 {
1886 BestiaryEntry bestiaryEntry = FindEntryByNPCID(item.Key);
1887 if (bestiaryEntry.Info.Contains(CommonTags.SpawnConditions.Events.Rain))
1888 {
1889 if (bestiaryEntry.Info.Contains(CommonTags.SpawnConditions.Biomes.Snow))
1890 {
1891 bestiaryEntry.AddTags(CommonTags.SpawnConditions.Visuals.Blizzard);
1892 }
1893 else
1894 {
1895 bestiaryEntry.AddTags(CommonTags.SpawnConditions.Visuals.Rain);
1896 }
1897 continue;
1898 }
1899 if (bestiaryEntry.Info.Contains(CommonTags.SpawnConditions.Events.Eclipse))
1900 {
1901 bestiaryEntry.AddTags(CommonTags.SpawnConditions.Visuals.EclipseSun);
1902 }
1903 if (bestiaryEntry.Info.Contains(CommonTags.SpawnConditions.Times.NightTime))
1904 {
1905 bestiaryEntry.AddTags(CommonTags.SpawnConditions.Visuals.Moon);
1906 }
1907 if (bestiaryEntry.Info.Contains(CommonTags.SpawnConditions.Times.DayTime))
1908 {
1909 bestiaryEntry.AddTags(CommonTags.SpawnConditions.Visuals.Sun);
1910 }
1911 if (bestiaryEntry.Info.Contains(CommonTags.SpawnConditions.Invasions.PumpkinMoon))
1912 {
1913 bestiaryEntry.AddTags(CommonTags.SpawnConditions.Visuals.PumpkinMoon);
1914 }
1915 if (bestiaryEntry.Info.Contains(CommonTags.SpawnConditions.Invasions.FrostMoon))
1916 {
1917 bestiaryEntry.AddTags(CommonTags.SpawnConditions.Visuals.FrostMoon);
1918 }
1919 if (bestiaryEntry.Info.Contains(CommonTags.SpawnConditions.Biomes.Meteor))
1920 {
1921 bestiaryEntry.AddTags(CommonTags.SpawnConditions.Visuals.Moon);
1922 bestiaryEntry.AddTags(CommonTags.SpawnConditions.Visuals.Meteor);
1923 }
1924 }
1925 }
